WEBVTT

00:01.596 --> 00:03.790
Mr. Harvey says that
Callie broke into his house.

00:03.797 --> 00:05.740
If the DA finds out,
you're gonna go to prison.

00:05.752 --> 00:07.634
There was more DNA on the murder weapon.

00:07.950 --> 00:09.320
Watch out!

00:09.355 --> 00:10.343
She's under arrest.

00:10.356 --> 00:11.722
Vehicular assault and
a felony hit and run.

00:11.725 --> 00:13.658
I know you killed your grandmother,
and we're gonna prove it.

00:13.693 --> 00:15.987
- You're crazy.
- I can't do this anymore.

00:16.032 --> 00:18.217
If you help us build a
case against your pimp,

00:18.244 --> 00:19.356
we're gonna put him behind bars.

00:19.379 --> 00:21.766
It's me, Diamond. You can come get me.

00:21.801 --> 00:24.820
There are so many unknowns
about traumatic brain injuries.

00:24.829 --> 00:26.076
- Emma's pregnant?
- No!

00:26.099 --> 00:27.772
She isn't pregnant anymore.

00:27.807 --> 00:30.045
I just can't face him and
not tell him the truth,

00:30.067 --> 00:31.626
so I wrote him this.

00:32.342 --> 00:33.838
You can't read it, can you?

00:33.860 --> 00:35.680
They're trying to turn Anchor
Beach into a private school.

00:35.715 --> 00:37.352
Wonder where this money is coming from.

00:37.388 --> 00:38.531
That's Craig Stratos.

00:38.541 --> 00:39.744
Did you hear about Anchor Beach?

00:39.762 --> 00:42.307
Frannie sent me a screen shot from
some anonymous Twitter account.

00:42.370 --> 00:44.010
I know you had an abortion,

00:44.037 --> 00:45.461
and that you didn't give Jesus a chance

00:45.462 --> 00:46.720
to tell you what he really wanted.

00:49.248 --> 00:50.284
Jesus?

00:51.464 --> 00:52.986
Jesus, are you listening to me?

00:54.768 --> 00:56.825
I can't afford to go to private school.

01:00.028 --> 01:01.676
You're pregnant, aren't you?

01:03.829 --> 01:05.682
Hey, hey, hey, hey, it's okay.

01:06.321 --> 01:07.448
It's okay.

01:07.898 --> 01:10.155
You know this might sound crazy, but...

01:10.362 --> 01:11.569
we can do this.

01:12.038 --> 01:13.092
I'm... I'm ready.

01:13.141 --> 01:15.137
We can have this baby together.

01:18.725 --> 01:20.258
I had an abortion.

01:22.947 --> 01:24.562
Why didn't you tell me?

01:24.597 --> 01:26.222
Why didn't you talk to me?

01:27.037 --> 01:29.757
I'm adopted, Emma, you know that.

01:31.018 --> 01:34.338
I didn't talk to you,
because the baby wasn't yours.

01:36.776 --> 01:38.193
It was Brandon's.

